The paper deals with an optimization problem in the context of online decision making, which is a common theme in the subfield of game theory (cs.GT) and online algorithms (cs.DS). The problem involves resource allocation, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses techniques from convex duality, which is a mathematical tool commonly used in information theory (cs.IT).
